V2: Rebase

Reviewed-by: Rodrigo Vivi <rodrigo.vivi@intel.com>
Link: https://patchwork.freedesktop.org/patch/msgid/9116319e7faceeed7695ee35e56fe001ddf94e11.1726151571.git.jani.nikula@intel.com
